        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3 class="footer-heads">Featured Tips</h3>
          <div id="tips">
            <h4>If someone you know has cancer:</h4>
            <ul id="dos-list">
              <li><strong>Do</strong> offer to listen. <p class="example">Example: "If you would like to talk about it, I am here."</p></li>
            </ul>
            <ul id="donts-list">
              <li><strong>Don't</strong> focus on appearances. <p class="example">Example: "Wow, you're losing a lot of weight!"</p></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/has_cancer" role="button" id="view-more">View more tips</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3 class="footer-heads">Someone...</h3>
          <ul id="browse-topics-footer">
